#. type: itemize
#: guix-git/doc/guix-cookbook.texi:4182
msgid "The dependencies of a project you are working on."
msgstr ""

#. type: itemize
#: guix-git/doc/guix-cookbook.texi:4185
msgid "Your favourite programming language libraries."
